name: Pineapple Crash into Lighthouse
description: Using Arnheim 1.0 described here https://www.chrisantha.co.uk/post/arnheim-1-0-overpainting-on-photographs and here https://arxiv.org/abs/2105.00162 this image maximizes the probability of "Pineapple Crash into Lighthouse" for an ALIGN trained Duel Encoder. It does not use a GAN, it uses a neural visual grammar system and evolution. The pineapple was not harmed, it didn't even really exist.
